node.text:
Since our storefront is currently closed on vacation, we have decided to giveaway a few knives to customers who shop / shopped online with us during our closure. Online orders over $100 placed between 7/30 and 8/11 will automatically be entered to win one of three knives!

1st- Mizuno Tanrenjo Aogami 2 Gyuto 270mm
2nd- Sakai Takayuki Shirogami 2 Hishigata 210mm (Togashi)
3rd- Kajiwara Kurouchi Aogami 2 Nakiri  165mm

Thank you for your support always, good luck!
#carbonknifeco #thankyou

*SHOP UPDATE*
Our storefront will be closed from July 30th through August 11th for a short break. Our online store will remain open as normal. We are a family owned business and taking this time to give ourselves and employees a well deserved break. Thank you for all of your support so far this year ❤. 
#carbonknifeco
